I"e<h2 id="inc">inc</h2>
<hr />
<p>컬럼타입이 int형인경우 일정 단위로 값을 증가할 수 있습니다.</p>

<div class="language-php highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1">// 숫자증가</span>
<span class="nv">$db</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">update</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"members3"</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">inc</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"click"</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">id</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">);</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>id=1 인 row의 click 필드값을 <code class="highlighter-rouge">+1</code> 증가합니다.
만일 다른 값을 증가하고자 할때에는 두번째 인자에 증가값을 설정합니다.</p>

<div class="language-php highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1">// 숫자증가</span>
<span class="nv">$db</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">update</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"members3"</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">inc</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"click"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">-&gt;</span><span class="na">id</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">);</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">+10</code>씩 값을 증가합니다.</p>
:ET